<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e115974.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Macrosemia fengi Wang sp. nov.: A, B habitus, holotype, ♂; C, D habitus, paratype, ♀; E fore femur, holotype, ♂. A, C dorsal views; B, D ventral views; E lateral view. Abbreviations: asp: apical spine; psp: primary spine; sasp: subapical spine; ssp: secondary spine. Scale bar a for A-D; b for E." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/970054" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e115974.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Macrosemia fengi Wang sp. nov., holotype, ♂: A-C abdominal sternite VIII; D-H pygofer; I-K aedeagus. A, D ventral views; B, E ventrolateral views; C, F, J lateral views; G, I dorsal views; H, K apical views. Abbreviations: aed: aedeagus; as: anal styles; ast: apical stylus; bl: basal lobe; ds: distal shoulder; uc: uncal clasper; un: uncus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/970058" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/BDJ.12.e115974.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Female terminalia of Macrosemia fengi Wang sp. nov., paratype: A dorsal view; B ventral view; C lateral view. Abbreviations: as: anal styles; db: dorsal beak; stVII: sternite VII; os: ovipositor sheath." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/975233" ;
